fields.content:
I am Khaja Mubashir Arsalan, an aspiring Data Scientist and Full-Stack Developer passionate about solving real-world problems through data-driven insights and scalable web solutions. Skilled in Machine Learning, Data Analysis, and Web Development, I specialize in building predictive models, creating interactive dashboards, and developing robust web applications. 

With hands-on experience in Python, SQL, Django, Tableau, Power BI, and Machine Learning frameworks, I enjoy working on projects that combine data science and software engineering to deliver impactful solutions.

fields.title: BACHOLER'S
fields.organization: TKR COLLEGE OF ENGINEERING AND TECHNOLOGY
fields.description: I have completed my B.Tech in Computer Science Engineering from TKR College of Engineering and Technology. My academic journey helped me build a solid foundation in programming, problem-solving, and developing innovative solutions

fields.title: INTERMEDIATE
fields.description: I have completed my Intermediate from Deeksha Junior College in the MPC stream, where I developed a strong foundation in Mathematics, which enhanced my analytical and problem-solving skills.

fields.title: SSC
fields.description: I have completed my Secondary School Certificate (SSC) from Mohammedia High School, which helped me build a strong academic foundation and develop essential learning skills.

fields.title: DATA SCIENCE INTERN
fields.description: I have completed my Data Science internship at Cognifyz Technologies, where I developed a Machine Learning model to predict restaurant ratings based on multiple independent variables. I used the Random Forest Regressor to achieve an accuracy of 85%, and after performing hyperparameter tuning, I successfully improved the model’s performance to around 89%.

fields.title: WEB DEVELOPER
fields.description: I have completed my internship at Systech Solutions as a Web Developer, where I developed the front-end of a recipe-sharing website using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. This project helped me enhance my skills in responsive design, user interface development, and creating interactive web pages.

fields.title: FULL STACK DEVELOPER
fields.description: I have completed my internship at EY as a Full Stack Developer, where I designed and developed an E-commerce website using Django, HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. I worked on implementing user authentication, product management, and gaining hands-on experience in building scalable and efficient web applications.

fields.name: KHAJA MUBASHIR ARSALAN
fields.description: Passionate Data Scientist and Full-Stack Developer with expertise in Machine Learning, Data Analysis, and Web Development. Skilled in Python, Django, SQL, and data visualization tools to build intelligent solutions. Experienced in developing predictive models, dashboards, and scalable web applications.

fields.title: Residential house price prediction using machine learning
fields.description: Build a user-friendly web-application where user can predict the prices of residential houses located in Bangalore. Based on the user's input it calculate the price of the house. Prices will be vary depends upon the user's input figures. This application uses CATBOOST (advance machine learning ensemble algorithm) which gather weak learner to create a strong learner.

fields.title: Restaurant rating prediction
fields.description: This application able to predict the restaurant rating depends upon the different factors. Based on that user can choose their specific restaurant. This application helpful for those user's who have not visited that specific restaurant yet and wanna know the ratings of that restaurant. This project uses advance machine learning ensemble technique called Random forest regressor for prediction.

fields.title: CR selection voting system
fields.description: Build a secure web-application for online voting of CR's. This application reduce the complexity of voting and enhance the transparency. This application allow students to vote remotely, even though they're not in the college boundries. It increase efficiency, time saving and it capable to show live results of the poling.

fields.title: Ecommerce website
fields.description: I developed a secure website for an e-commerce platform that enables users to search a wide variety of products while providing a live tracking system. Administrators can manage the entire inventory, and the system facilitates users in submitting valuable feedback to sellers, who receive this feedback directly via email.

fields.title: Tailor billing web application
fields.description:
This application has been specifically developed for our client, who owns a tailoring shop. Previously, they relied on a traditional bill book to manage their records. The website is divided into two main sections: one for employees and one for the shop owner. Employees have access to the billing and record-keeping pages, while the admin can view a detailed Profit and Loss (P&L) page.

This website allows our client to manage their records in a modern and efficient manner. The admin can search for records based on bill numbers, and the ability to share invoices with customers via email and WhatsApp are among the outstanding features of this application.
